      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Distributed Systems - first hard truth\n    - ALL DATA IS CACHED AND SUSPECT*\n    - All data is immutable - read only. Don't change it.\n    - The service is the only thing that can change it.\n\n    * exception: the actual bits on the hard drive of your database.",
